Project Overview
This project is a Portfolio Webpage built with HTML and CSS. It showcases my profile, skills, and projects in a clean and professional format. The repo is hosted on GitHub (csf-assignment) and developed using VS Code with Git for version control.

Development Process
 Created a GitHub repo and initialized Git locally.
 Built webpage structure in index.html and styled with style.css.
 Tested in browser using VS Code.
 Used Git commands (add, commit, push) to upload changes.
 Added .gitignore, README.md, and a docs/ folder for documentation.

Future Improvements
 Make the webpage responsive for mobile devices.
 Add JavaScript for interactivity (dark mode, animations).
 Deploy using GitHub Pages for public access.
 Expand content with more projects and achievements.
